					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Derivative of x<sup>n</sup> = n·x<sup>n-1</sup><br /><br />Do it again: n·(n-1)·x<sup>n-2</sup><br />And again: n·(n-1)·(n-2)·x<sup>n-3</sup><br /><br />Looks like factorial, no?</div>

